<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1906-03-16T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1906-03-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="512" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d512">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">O’Brien</persName> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi>.</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Montevideo,
                                        Uruguay</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-03-16"><hi rend="italic">March 16,
                                1906</hi></date>.</dateline>
                            <seg rendition="#left">No. 99.]</seg></opener>
                        <p><hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to advise you that I have
                            received a personal note from the minister of foreign affairs relating
                            to your acceptance of Uruguay’s invitation, a copy of which is herewith
                            inclosed.</p>
                        <p>I am, etc.,</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Edward C.
                            O’Brien.</hi></signed></closer>
                        <frus:attachment>
                            <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Inclosure.]</seg></opener>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Minister of Foreign
                                        Relations</gloss> to Minister <persName type="to">O’Brien</persName></hi>.</head>
                            <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Montevideo</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-03-15"><hi rend="italic">March 15,
                                        1906</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                            <p><hi rend="smallcaps">Dear Mr. Minister</hi>: With my best compliments
                                I can inform you that yesterday at 11 p.m. I received from
                                Washington the following cablegram: <quote rend="blockquote">
                                    <p>Secretary accepts with especial thanks. I made him aware of
                                        initiative.</p>
                                    <p rend="right">(Signed) <hi rend="smallcaps">Requena
                                            Bermudez.</hi></p>
                                </quote></p>
                            <p>Yours, most truly,</p>
                            <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">José Romeu.</hi></signed></closer>
                        </frus:attachment>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>